                <p class="card-text">
                    Using ContactMVC is easy.  Create categories as tags for your contacts.  Create contacts
                    and link them to your tags.
                </p>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Contacts are searchable and can be edited or deleted, just like categories.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
